        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2661037481" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14675242692404156875">This was an excellent read when I was a teenager and beginning to absorb the classic albums and learn the history of heavy metal. Going back to it today is admittedly hard as a learned fan because it focuses way too hard on the biggest-name bands, but it does an admirable job of covering all the sub genres. If this was ever updated for the last 20 years (djent, atmo-black, etc) I would read it again.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


